name: Laura Nelson
description: Every one of us has suffered romantic setbacks in our lives or else we would not be here seeking a partner. The ability to maintain a joy for life in the face of these setbacks is very important to me. I prefer being out and about enjoying a glass of wine. The words typically used to describe me are fun, infectious (and yes, that is a good thing!), sensitive, loyal, classy, honest, creative, welcoming, down to earth and personable. I am a bit of a chameleon so put me in the middle of most situations and I’ll rise to the challenge..
